{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"60afbd4f-ce4b-4bce-9088-d72ee3d41880","content":"No repo-specific pipeline exists, so here's the general guidance:\n\n## Migrating from VSTest@3 to Microsoft.Testing.Platform\n\n### 1. Update your test project\n\nIn your `.csproj`, enable the new platform:\n\n```xml\n<PropertyGroup>\n  <EnableMSTestRunner>true</EnableMSTestRunner>\n  <OutputType>Exe</OutputType>\n</PropertyGroup>\n```\n\n### 2. Replace `VSTest@3` with `DotNetCoreCLI@2` (or a script)\n\n```yaml\n- task: DotNetCoreCLI@2\n  displayName: 'Run Tests'\n  inputs:\n    command: 'run'\n    projects: '**/*Tests.csproj'\n    arguments: >\n      --\n      --results-directory $(Agent.TempDirectory)\n      --report-trx\n      --coverage\n      --coverage-output-format cobertura\n```\n\nOr use a script step for more control:\n\n```yaml\n- script: >\n    dotnet test MyTests.csproj\n    --results-directory $(Agent.TempDirectory)\n    --report-trx\n    --coverage\n    --coverage-output-format cobertura\n  displayName: 'Run Tests (Microsoft.Testing.Platform)'\n```\n\n### 3. Publish TRX results\n\n```yaml\n- task: PublishTestResults@2\n  inputs:\n    testResultsFormat: 'VSTest'\n    testResultsFiles: '$(Agent.TempDirectory)/**/*.trx'\n```\n\n### 4. Publish code coverage\n\n```yaml\n- task: PublishCodeCoverageResults@2\n  inputs:\n    codeCoverageToolType: 'Cobertura'\n    summaryFileLocation: '$(Agent.TempDirectory)/**/*.cobertura.xml'\n```\n\n### Key differences from VSTest@3\n\n| Concern | Old (VSTest@3) | New (Testing.Platform) |\n|---------|---------------|----------------------|\n| Runner | `vstest.console.exe` | Test project is an exe itself |\n| TRX | Built-in `--logger trx` | `--report-trx` CLI arg |\n| Coverage | `--collect \"Code Coverage\"` | `--coverage` CLI arg |\n| Task | `VSTest@3` | `DotNetCoreCLI@2` or `script` |\n\nThe `--report-trx` and `--coverage` flags are native to Microsoft.Testing.Platform — no extra adapters needed.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"463538ed-4d29-42f9-a95e-032299db032e","outputTokens":599,"requestId":"6819:1242BB:756357:7C99D0:6A044D52"},"id":"7dbfa091-f52e-4f28-839f-4b21112e05ad","timestamp":"2026-05-13T10:07:28.171Z","parentId":"1babb86f-fa64-437c-b083-b5e0faad1e04"}
